Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.15,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么搞的 闪一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.07,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,走开啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:43.98,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.67,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼啊
